data.description: It's all about the options! That's what you'll get in this gorgeous townhouse.  Primary residence, short term rental or investment property.  Built in 2018 means you'll have the energy efficiency and latest construction standards to save you money and give you piece of mind.  This 3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom home has an open concept kitchen featuring crown molding and custom, solid-cherry soft-closing drawers and upgraded granite countertops.  Upgraded cabinetry continues upstairs with the vanities in both bathrooms.  Backyard is fully fenced and ready to go.  Washer and Dryer will stay with the home.  Whether you are a first time buyer, downsizing or looking to invest... don't look past Sound Haven Ct.
